    | CHECKPOINT
    | CLASS
    | CLOSE
    | CLUSTER
    | COLUMNS
    | COMMENT
    | COMMENTS
    | COMMIT
    | COMMITTED
    | CONFIGURATION
    | CONFLICT
    | CONNECTION
    | CONSTRAINTS
    | CONTENT
    | CONTINUE
    | CONVERSION
    | COPY
