    | OPTION
    | OPTIONS
    | ORDINALITY
    | OTHERS
    | OVER
    | OVERRIDING
    | OWNED
    | OWNER
    | PARALLEL
    | PARSER
    | PARTIAL
    | PARTITION
    | PASSING
    | PASSWORD
    | PLANS
    | POLICY
    | PRECEDING
    | PREPARE
    | PREPARED
    | PRESERVE
    | PRIOR
    | PRIVILEGES
    | PROCEDURAL
    | PROCEDURE
    | PROCEDURES
    | PROGRAM
    | PUBLICATION
    | QUOTE
    | RANGE
    | READ
    | REASSIGN
    | RECHECK
    | RECURSIVE
    | REF
    | REFERENCING
    | REFRESH
    | REINDEX
    | RELATIVE
    | RELEASE
    | RENAME
    | REPEATABLE
    | REPLACE
    | REPLICA
    | RESET
    | RESTART
    | RESTRICT
    | RETURNS
    | REVOKE
    | ROLE
    | ROLLBACK
    | ROLLUP
    | ROUTINE
    | ROUTINES
