    | RULE
    | SAVEPOINT
    | SCHEMA
    | SCHEMAS
    | SCROLL
    | SEARCH
    | SECOND
    | SECURITY
    | SEQUENCE
    | SEQUENCES
    | SERIALIZABLE
    | SERVER
    | SESSION
